tactic: destruct (list_bool_decomp k lb) as [[ln [lc [Heq Hvalid]]] | [ln [r [Heq [Hvalid Hex]]]]].
exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 2 branches.

original: destruct (list_bool_decomp k lb) as [[ln [lc [Heq Hvalid]]] | [ln [r [Heq [Hvalid Hex]]]]]. - left. exists ln. split. + apply Heq. + apply Hvalid. - right. exists ln. exists (list_repeat Zero (S r)). + split. * apply Heq. * left. apply (proj1 Hvalid).
